{"tid":82393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[青政正式收皮]上訴庭駁回梁游上訴至終院申請 須付政府訟費","createTime":"2017-01-16T02:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T05:52:49.000Z","uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"760eee007c1be07953e9fdd4d671dc7add180bbe","tid":82393,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170116/s00001/1484530354145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170116%2Fs00001%2F1484530354145&d=KPPkmUstXgKNlaWvbQeyJmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=5ea3063b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170116%2Fs00001%2F1484530354145&h=7f4cc012\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170116/s00001/1484530354145</a><br />\n<br />\n上訴庭駁回梁頌恆游蕙禎上訴至終院申請　兩人須付政府訟費 (09:31)"},{"pid":"0ce57327e226a138b9c4c62d5f64aaf833a327ee","tid":82393,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T02:07:01.000Z","msg":"青年新政梁頌恆和游蕙禎早前被高等法院裁定宣誓無效，取消二人立法會議員資格，梁游其後提出上訴被駁回，兩人早前再向上訴庭申請終院上訴許可。上訴庭今早頒下判辭，拒絕批出上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭亦頒令，梁游一方須付政府訟費，梁游各須付約16.8萬元。"},{"pid":"5538fdc1e5cd0bc13e727b3676c552c409c0123e","tid":82393,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e829eeab6e868115a5a4cb6ddf5c58f16c1c5e7","tid":82393,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"香港玩完就真"},{"pid":"1d11e574c493048c2a5109eaf315567153daa0c7","tid":82393,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"係咪玩完？"},{"pid":"2a0974e2e28c519ed73607ec84f47761efb6dccf","tid":82393,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi